Titolo: Nanotale - Typing Chronicles

Anno: 2021

Descrizione: Nanotale - Typing Chronicles is a fantasy adventure and typing video game developed and published by Fishing Cactus and released from early access on March 31, 2021 for Windows and Stadia. It is the second game in the Typing Chronicles series after Epistory - Typing Chronicles. The main character is Rosalind, an archivist with a talent for word magic. It received mixed reviews from critics, who praised its world design, lore, and mechanics, but criticized the story as weak.